{
  "title": "Icons & Signage",
  "slug": "brand/icons-and-signage",
  "parent": "brand",
  "summary": "Using icons and pictograms in the right way can help navigate through certain environments.",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Icons & Signage",
      "tag": "H2",
      "max-width": true,
      "cols": "1",
      "columns": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "tag": "p",
          "text": "Using icons and pictograms in the right way can help navigate through certain environments."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "In communication",
      "tag": "H2",
      "max-width": true,
      "cols": "1",
      "columns": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "tag": "p",
          "text": "When we use icons in communication we have selected a few that can help to lead the viewer and convey the message as clearly as possible. Icons are a great communicative tool to guide the eye and highlight certain actions."
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "/assets/brand-hub/958f4523-406b-4768-ba81-01f42d119657.png"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "/assets/brand-hub/88772cc1-3b66-4e0b-a0f9-c8e14b1ccfb2.gif"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "/assets/brand-hub/52574459-8ce3-4387-8a39-84cf069e6efc.jpeg"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Real estate",
      "tag": "H2",
      "max-width": true,
      "cols": "1",
      "columns": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "tag": "p",
          "text": "When it comes to navigating a building we need to keep accessibility in mind. That’s why real estate will be the only place we use our pictograms, eg. toilets, recycling, coffee, floors, elevators."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "tag": "p",
          "text": "These are the collection of pictograms real estate can choose from."
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "/assets/brand-hub/d7bce8b1-01d7-4123-b5df-96bd1bf8ec38.png"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "/assets/brand-hub/d25fd74c-f595-4983-abd3-ba7dd83c4299.jpeg"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Download",
      "tag": "H2",
      "max-width": true,
      "cols": "1",
      "columns": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "tag": "p",
          "text": "Here you'll find the entire icons package. Be mindful of how you use them. A picture or good wording is usually more substantial than using an icon."
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "/assets/brand-hub/af01de50-8fa3-49b3-8fe7-78759061012a.svg"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "tag": "p",
          "text": "DoUse the icons in our library."
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "/assets/brand-hub/a6ea817b-5edb-4f00-859c-528a1bacb110.jpeg"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "tag": "p",
          "text": "Don'tNever use any other icons."
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "/assets/brand-hub/ef093eb3-c74e-49aa-913c-037e883d066a.svg"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "tag": "p",
          "text": "DoSize icons seen together to have equal stroke width."
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "/assets/brand-hub/c306872e-056d-4e6d-8e86-fe433289f52f.svg"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "tag": "p",
          "text": "Don'tDon't mix stroke width and sizes."
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "/assets/brand-hub/cfe8d279-ddc5-4942-87fd-35e9d279d45c.svg"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "tag": "p",
          "text": "DoScale icons evenly."
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "/assets/brand-hub/47c885ac-33c9-46d4-9643-5df7508344f3.svg"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "tag": "p",
          "text": "Don'tNever resize the icons unevenly."
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "/assets/brand-hub/9b66cbb8-934d-40c2-a76c-64e2acf527bc.svg"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "tag": "p",
          "text": "DoUse icons together with text."
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "/assets/brand-hub/909dee3c-ebc1-48f1-8e7d-070077915d12.svg"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "tag": "p",
          "text": "Don'tNever combine icons in an effort to give them new meaning."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "tag": "p",
          "text": "Previous chapter"
        }
      ]
    },
